    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine state, smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been meticulously stored and maintained to the highest standards. A buyer can expect a car that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it was first delivered.",
