    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear. Every mechanical component has been meticulously maintained, and all features function perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in such an impeccable state.",
      "price": 49500.0,
